matlab tools to create embedded configuration:

findgridpos.m : help tune the position of the embedded grid into
the parent grid 

nested_grid.m : do the embedded grid

nested_forcing.m : do the forcing file

nested_oa.m : do the oa files (if any...)

nested_initial.m : do the initial file (if not using the oa files)

nested_clim.m : do the climatology file

test_grid.m : test the grid

test_forcing.m : test the forcing file

test_clim.m : test the climatology file


